t;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/vdohnovenie&quot;&gt;Вдохновение&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/ironiya&quot;&gt;Ирония&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/torzhestvennost&quot;&gt;Торжественность&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
